ags:resource.dc:description: DEM from multibeam echosounder data gathered on board R/V Ramón Margalef during IEO Bimbache cruises

Video showing a virtual flight through El Hierro volcano and its deposits of pyroclasts and cinder through the submarine canyon that constrain them to the abyssal plain where they finally are extended in a wide fan.
